設站設有兩個較短的[[側式月台|側式月台]]和兩條軌道，月台有效長度為約6節（但只有前5節開門，因為每列{{link-en|紐約地鐵R62型列車|R62 (New York City Subway car)|R62型}}列車在行駛3號線列車時必須同時開門）<ref name=NYAmsterdam-145thLenox-1967>{{cite web |last1=Edwards |first1=Dick |title=145th-Lenox Subway Stop To Continue |url=http://media.proquest.com/media/pq/hnp/doc/1043451842/fmt/ai/rep/NONE?hl=subways%2Csubway%2Csubways%2Csubway%2C145th+street%2Clenox+avenue&cit%3Aauth=Edwards%2C+Dick&cit%3Atitle=145th-Lenox+Subway+Stop+To+Continue&cit%3Apub=New+York+Amsterdam+News+%281962-1993%29&cit%3Avol=&cit%3Aiss=&cit%3Apg=3&cit%3Adate=Dec+2%2C+1967&ic=true&cit%3Aprod=ProQuest+Historical+Newspapers%3A+New+York+Amsterdam+News&_%3D%3D&_s=ANffqswLiVm2%2FUlPdIVNQ6yx%2Fz0%3D#statusbar=1&zoom=150 |publisher=[[New_York_Amsterdam_News|New York Amsterdam News]] |accessdate=10 July 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710091610/http://media.proquest.com/media/pq/hnp/doc/1043451842/fmt/ai/rep/NONE?hl=subways%2Csubway%2Csubways%2Csubway%2C145th%2Bstreet%2Clenox%2Bavenue&cit%3Aauth=Edwards%2C%2BDick&cit%3Atitle=145th-Lenox%2BSubway%2BStop%2BTo%2BContinue&cit%3Apub=New%2BYork%2BAmsterdam%2BNews%2B%281962-1993%29&cit%3Avol=&cit%3Aiss=&cit%3Apg=3&cit%3Adate=Dec%2B2%2C%2B1967&ic=true&cit%3Aprod=ProQuest%2BHistorical%2BNewspapers%3A%2BNew%2BYork%2BAmsterdam%2BNews&_%3D%3D&_s=ANffqswLiVm2%2FUlPdIVNQ6yx%2Fz0%3D#statusbar=1&zoom=150 |archivedate=2015-07-10 |date=December 2, 1967 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>。曾經一度只有4節開門，直至2002年3號線列車運動每列9節的{{link-en|紐約地鐵R62A型列車|R62A (New York City Subway car)|R62A型}}列車。

與其他{{link-en|IRT地鐵早期歷史|Early history of the IRT subway|原初IRT地鐵}}車站相同，起初設計只停靠比現時地鐵8至10節列車為短的列車。最終，其餘車站皆被延長月台或直接關閉，145街車站與[[南碼頭-白廳街車站#舊站|南碼頭迴圈車站]]成為唯二仍不能停靠10節列車的原初IRT車站。車站北面是一個剪式橫渡線，以便在3號線北端總站[[哈萊姆-148街車站_(IRT萊諾克斯大道線)|哈萊姆-148街車站]]靠站。車站南面是與[[IRT白原路線|IRT白原路線]]連接的{{link-en|142街交匯處|142nd Street Junction}}。車站不延長的主因是因為兩個方向都距離轉轍器太近，雖然將轉轍器北移並不昂貴。

